        "Description": "Greetings, 47.\r\rYour targets are wealthy Marrakech landlord Nimr &apos;Arif Bahar and Danish drifter Sebastian Krogh. The two have conspired to murder Krogh’s mother—an heiress to a dormant family fortune—in exchange for a substantial payout. Surveillance confirms they’ve begun final preparations and are currently planning to meet in the old city&apos;s bazaar. Prevent the crime before it’s committed.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
